ygData.messageBody:
WTF!! Which in this case means Way Too Funny.
This was funny the first time, but even better as a
"rip off." <br><br>What sever? Tunare? or is that just
your wonderful choice of godess? <br><br>High Elf
Karioke is on Friday Nights in the Felwithe Cleric Guild.
Keep it clean though, those High Elf clerics are very
pious and don't take kindly to all that rock and roll.
(Notice how there are no High Elf Bards??) "What are you
kids listening too? That's Innorruk
music!!!!"<br><br>Xela Orcbane<br>Druid of the 35th
prayer<br>Xev<br><br>"I'm 35 now, but still fight, drink, play, and smith
like a teenager!!"<br>"Is that a good thing??"
